        <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed">Disclaimer: Calculators provide estimates only and should not be used as financial, tax, or medical advice. Always consult a qualified professional. Australian tax rates based on ATO published rates for the current financial year. CalculatorMate is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program.</p>
